Keep this image EXACTLY the same - same neon wireframe banana, same dark purple/black background, 
    same cyan/magenta/yellow color scheme, same holographic grid effects, same composition.
    
    The ONLY change: make the text 'NANO BANANA PRO FOR PRODUCT MANAGERS' MUCH LARGER so it's readable as a small thumbnail.
    
    Do not add any extra text, badges, or elements. Just enlarge the existing text.
